decks.notes: This deck focuses on controlling the game by countering spells and removing threats while gradually building up its own board presence. It utilizes a mix of efficient counterspells like Force of Will and Mana Leak, along with versatile removal spells like Swords to Plowshares and Skyclave Apparition. The Commander, Aragorn, King of Gondor, provides a powerful aggro threat that can close out games quickly if left unchecked. The deck also includes cards like Teferi, Time Raveler and Spell Queller to disrupt the opponent's game plan and maintain tempo. Overall, the strategy revolves around disrupting the opponent's plays, controlling the board, and finishing off the game with powerful threats.
